  "2326200": {
    "name": "NEO BERLIN 2087",
    "steam_appid": 2326200,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/91bd948caa8890249a6e7348413c1cad.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" width=592 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/91bd948caa8890249a6e7348413c1cad.webm?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/91bd948caa8890249a6e7348413c1cad.mp4?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事大纲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事始于一个阴森恐怖的夜晚，新柏林因警察局长惨遭谋杀而陷入混乱。才华洋溢但背负着阴暗过去的神秘侦探诺兰，接下了艰巨的任务──寻找并保护局长的女儿娜塔莉，因为他将会是解开父亲死亡之谜的关键。凭借着最先进的技术、武器和独特能力，诺兰踏上危险的旅程，誓言尽快找到娜塔莉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/9272f6171d1d2ccff9cdfc7d4beb711f.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/9272f6171d1d2ccff9cdfc7d4beb711f.webm?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/9272f6171d1d2ccff9cdfc7d4beb711f.mp4?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但诺兰踏出的每一步，都让他更接近一场足以吞噬他与整座城市的邪恶阴谋。当他终于与个性独立且足智多谋的娜塔莉正面相遇时，他也意识到两人的命运早已以他无法想像的方式相连在一起。他们的关系由爱、恐惧与不确定交织而成。在前方的险恶道路上，他们被迫面对内心最深沉的恐惧，对抗那些企图摧毁他们的黑暗势力。这是一个扣人心弦且充满情感张力的故事，描述阴谋与背叛，其叙事风格将会让你从头到尾都坐立难安。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/2d035d9a06b88622563d03579d8dbe1a.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" width=592 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/2d035d9a06b88622563d03579d8dbe1a.webm?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/2d035d9a06b88622563d03579d8dbe1a.mp4?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市远远矗立在荒原之上，如同一座闪耀而坚不可摧的堡垒。高耸的城墙隔绝了外界与城内，下方的街道充斥着分裂社会的喧嚣与熙攘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/0971b2b1421e35aee8954b3cca2036c0.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" width=592 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/0971b2b1421e35aee8954b3cca2036c0.webm?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/0971b2b1421e35aee8954b3cca2036c0.mp4?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Neo Berlin 2087这个技术进步与机械化改造的时代，富人统治着城市，他们的权力绝对且无可挑战。他们生活在奢华之中，身边充斥着最进步且尖端的科技，而穷人则在贫民窟艰难求生，为每一口食物、每一丝希望努力挣扎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个对比鲜明的世界，光明与黑暗并存，希望与绝望交织。然而，即使是在混乱与暴力之中，仍有人拒绝放弃，挺身对抗压迫者，为自己的信念而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场关于正义、友情、爱情、愧疚、牺牲与背叛的旅程。主角等人将在旅途中接受考验，其决心会被逼至极限，因为他们将面对那些想要毁灭他们的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/bbf900f26416beb0a9b0a533180bd262.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" width=592 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/bbf900f26416beb0a9b0a533180bd262.webm?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/bbf900f26416beb0a9b0a533180bd262.mp4?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演身为侦探的主角，能以常人无法达到的方式揭开真相。你拥有理解人类行为、寻找破案线索的独特洞察力，甚至可以透过骇入嫌疑人的心智来获取有价值的信息。每一种情绪、每一个想法、每一段记忆都是拼图的一部分，帮助你伸张正义，揭穿隐藏的秘密。尽管要在复杂的社会与政治环境中前行将充满挑战，但你对正义的执着从未动摇。你准备好接受调查员的挑战，为这座城市中最需要正义的人们伸张正义了吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/2a1acdabe3dd467c4e659f0304667767.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" width=592 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/2a1acdabe3dd467c4e659f0304667767.webm?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/2a1acdabe3dd467c4e659f0304667767.mp4?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >荒原</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在执行任务时也会穿越荒原──这里不仅是流放者的家园，也是失控机器的栖息地，这些机器因程式故障而发展出自己的生命，在大地上漫无目的地游荡。<br>在那里几乎没有任何生命，只有小规模的生态系统和稀少的饮用水。<br>流放者居住在自己搭建的小型聚落或洞穴中，分裂成不同派系，宛如地下组织。<br>废弃的聚落或许是不错的食物来源，弹药和机械零件则可以在荒原各处找到，用于升级装备。机器敌人掉落机械零件的机率更高，但也更难击败──尤其在夜间，它们的数量会更多，而人类敌人则在白天比较常见。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/36d17d9396ba864c7858daa80f296d1f.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" width=592 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/36d17d9396ba864c7858daa80f296d1f.webm?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/36d17d9396ba864c7858daa80f296d1f.mp4?t=1764605317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >情感丰富的主线故事，包含艰难的道德选择与身历其境的调查玩法。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的游戏体验，结合第一与第三人称视角，可自订角色的能力与武器，打造符合你的喜好的游玩风格，可自由选择丰富的射击、潜行和角色扮演游戏机制。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感源自经典的赛博朋克电影与主题。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索你从未见过的场景：2087年的柏林，一座被巨大的新柏林围墙包覆的赛博朋克大都会，城墙外是流放者聚集的荒原，以及游荡的故障机器。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充满危险敌人的荒原，体验无以伦比的真实感。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在刺激的战斗场景中考验你的反应能力，或以更隐密的方式避免正面冲突。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/987175e515266569ec8b5e4f23a35268.webp?t=1764605317\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326200/extras/987175e515266569ec8b5e4f23a35268.poster.avif?t=1764605317\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=250 /></picture></span></p>",
